title: Sara Yuceil
text:
Sara Yüceil (born 22 June 1988) is a <a href="Belgium">Belgian</a> <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> midfielder who plays for <a href="PSV%20Vrouwen">PSV</a> in the Dutch <a href="Eredivisie%20Women">Eredivisie Women</a>. She played for <a href="Standard%20Li%C3%A8ge%20%28women%29">Standard Liège</a> and <a href="Oud-Heverlee%20Leuven%20%28women%29">OH Leuven</a> in Belgium before moving to France.
Honours.
Winner
